<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829924>
    dc:description "Figs 37–56. Trechus spp., aedeagal median lobe, left lateral view (37, 39, 40, 42, 44–45, 47–48, 50, 52–53, 55–56) and dorsal view (38, 41, 43, 46, 49, 51, 54). 37–38. T. mattisi sp. nov., paratype. 39. T. transversicollis sp. nov., holotype. 40–41. T. minitrechus sp. nov., paratype. 42–43. T. nanulus sp. nov., paratype. 44. T. rira sp. nov., holotype. 45–46. T. iridescens sp. nov., holotype. 47. T. relictus Magrini, Quéinnec & Vigna Taglianti, 2012, specimen from brook valley above Goba. 48–49. T. oppositus sp. nov., paratype. 50–51. T. harryi sp. nov., paratype. 52. T. dodola sp. nov., holotype. 53–54. T. adaba sp. nov., paratype. 55. T. harenna sp. nov., paratype. 56. T. bombi sp. nov., holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3829924/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829932>
    dc:description "Figs 71–74. Trechus spp., head, pronotum. 71. T. depressipennis sp. nov., holotype. 72. T. mekbibi sp. nov., paratype, ³. 73. T. hagenia sp. nov., paratype, ³. 74. T. colobus sp. nov., paratype, ³." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3829932/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829938>
    dc:description "Figs 83–86. Trechus spp., head, pronotum. 83. T. wiersbowskyi sp. nov., paratype, ³. 84. T. grandipennis sp. nov., holotype. 85. T. sanettii sp. nov., paratype, ³. 86. T. abalkhasimi sp. nov., paratype, ³." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3829938/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829944>
    dc:description "Figs 95–98. Trechus spp., head, pronotum. 95. T. fisehai sp. nov., paratype, ³. 96. T. angavoensis sp. nov., holotype. 97. T. batuensis Magrini & Sciaky, 2006, ³ from Sanetti Plateau near Tulo Dimptu. 98. T. batuensis, ³ from Tegona Valley." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3829944/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829950>
    dc:description "Figs 107–110. Trechus spp., head, pronotum. 107. T. haggei sp. nov., paratype, ³. 108. T. tragelaphus sp. nov., holotype. 109. T. nigrifemoralis, sp. nov., holotype. 110. T. balesilvestris, sp. nov., holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3829950/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829954>
    dc:description "Figs 115–125. Trechus spp., aedeagal median lobe, left lateral view (115–116, 118, 120, 122, 124–125) and dorsal view (117, 119, 121, 123). 115. T. depressipennis sp. nov., holotype. 116–117. T. mekbibi sp. nov., paratypes. 118–119. T. hagenia sp. nov., paratypes. 120–121. T. colobus sp. nov., paratypes. 122–123. T. wiersbowskyi sp. nov., paratypes. 124. T. haggei sp. nov., paratype. 125. T. grandipennis sp. nov., holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3829954/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829956>
    dc:description "Figs 126–137. Trechus spp., aedeagal median lobe, left lateral view (126, 128–129, 131, 133, 135–137) and dorsal view (127, 130, 132, 134). 126–127. T. sanettii sp. nov., paratypes. 128. T. angavoensis sp. nov., holotype. 129–130. T. batuensis Magrini & Sciaky, 2006, specimens from Wasama Valley. 131–132. T. abalkhasimi sp. nov., paratypes. 133–134. T. fisehai sp. nov., paratypes. 135. T. tragelaphus sp. nov., holotype. 136. T. nigrifemoralis sp. nov., holotype. 137. T. balesilvestris sp. nov., holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3829956/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

